n重組鄂圖曼帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n凱末爾激到番生未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係九泉之下吐血中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84c8d9e22107d6b2fbdf2451a0bb9e10f866fee","tid":223104,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"學埋支那啲9野"},{"pid":"b0d11c51a72d7545147639343b5bfa755da5351e","tid":223104,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成個宗教世族化唔到, 玩完.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無世俗回大國？<br />\n哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3521c22e827960be65d12b8151d4e05e7919f160","tid":223104,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7079c64e71d1be2c2bcbbad9a5d8f8c8b43c2734","tid":223104,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"啲回撚全部垃圾"},{"pid":"c7fe22e28372ef97533ebd17b3bfc1f5b472a762","tid":223104,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成個宗教世族化唔到, 玩完.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無世俗回大國？<br />\n哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬來西亞，孟加拉，印尼，呢三個算唔算？"},{"pid":"cf5ef05acda4d9a16e1a5ba815ab6b1b5d726236","tid":223104,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成個宗教世族化唔到, 玩完.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無世俗回大國？<br />\n哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印尼馬拉都算既掛? 因為亞洲同中亞 (中東) 有距離.<br />\n但係中亞非洲呢 D 有陸上連結又貧窮既國家就死晒. <br />\n<br />\n唔貧窮但富有就更深信不二. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返東歐前蘇聯加盟國可以吊下癮.<br />\n<br />\n回教係全世界養大, 所有石油消耗國養大沙地同縱容佢用原教法 (斬手腳, 問吊) 令到呢 d 思潮不斷.  <br />\n<br />\n淨係脫教要死同聖戰呢兩樣野已經令回教屈晒機. 原教旨意另到科學不能倡明, 對女性抑壓蔑視亦都催化成個社會既暴戾. 講佢地係毒瘤並唔係歧視而成.<br />\n<br />\n當年英意成功推動世俗化對我地現代社會功不可沒, 亞洲受古中國影響既國家就好彩無比回教淹蓋."},{"pid":"30ee367ef447810ad216d5bcfd5b9329a5c44d23","tid":223104,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"又一次人類文明倒退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估下班難民向東走定向西走喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d77f0d4ca1e0383fcb84234edfe2fae0dc0f27","tid":223104,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:19:11.000Z","msg":"我仲想去火雞國架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fd7884ae083f087071087237ca775586c6ad4b","tid":223104,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:25:15.000Z","msg":"又返轉頭"},{"pid":"db00daa58647761a2525b5179c907960d89e80ee","tid":223104,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成個宗教世族化唔到, 玩完.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有無世俗回大國？<br />\n哈薩克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印尼馬拉都算既掛? 因為亞洲同中亞 (中東) 有距離.<br />\n但係中亞非洲呢 D 有陸上連結又貧窮既國家就死晒. <br />\n<br />\n唔貧窮但富有就更深信不二. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返東歐前蘇聯加盟國可以吊下癮.<br />\n<br />\n回教係全世界養大, 所有石油消耗國養大沙地同縱容佢用原教法 (斬手腳, 問吊) 令到呢 d 思潮不斷.  <br />\n<br />\n淨係脫教要死同聖戰呢兩樣野已經令回教屈晒機. 原教旨意另到科學不能倡明, 對女性抑壓蔑視亦都催化成個社會既暴戾. 講佢地係毒瘤並唔係歧視而成.<br />\n<br />\n當年英意成功推動世俗化對我地現代社會功不可沒, 亞洲受古中國影響既國家就好彩無比回教淹蓋.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印尼近期選省長都有少少倒退跡象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢到係人民有原教旨復興，<br />\n佐科維多多好似都仲幾世俗支持鍾萬學呢位基督徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a71bc443f698effbc659d3de23113d7378bf2a","tid":223104,"uid":47641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"凱末爾辛辛苦苦積落既遺產就快冇唒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be59bfb6835a21f0ab572d65a4b2775d64f06e6","tid":223104,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"閪亞狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a74ad9f7014b667d67b1f074799986fca71f2ce","tid":223104,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"回豬不嬲都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e002087c5d0f6e6553a92983bcad6524a236baf1","tid":223104,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"回教同伊斯蘭教有咩分别？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}